modName: Craftable Panties Bras and Stockings for CBBEv3M
summary: This mod adds different craftable panties, bras and stockings to the game, based on MAK\'s models for his CBBEv3M body
descriptionHtml:
[img]http://i183.photobucket.com/albums/x302/gotha83/nexus/craftablepantys.png[/img]
HI, this is my first MOD I\'m releasing xD
looking forward for feedback :)


[img]http://i183.photobucket.com/albums/x302/gotha83/nexus/description.png[/img]
This MOD adds different craftable panties, bras and stockings to the game, based on MAK\'s CBBEv3M Body. 
Basically, now you can change them ingame, without messing around with textures, just put another on :P

- Panty: Black, Blue, Green, Darker Green, Orange, Pink, Purple, Grey, Red, Dark Red, White, Leather, Native
- You find em @ [b]Tanning Rack[/b], called [b]*Panty: (Color)*[/b]

- Amiella Panty: Black, Blue, Green, Darker Green, Grey, Orange, Pink, Red, Dark Red, White, Leather
- You find em@ [b]Tanning Rack[/b], called [b]*Amiella Panty: (Color)*[/b]

- Lacy Panty in many colors
- You find em@ [b]Tanning Rack[/b], called [b]*Lacy Panty: (Color)*[/b]

- Stockings in many colors
- You find em@ [b]Tanning Rack[/b], called [b]*Stockings: (Color)*[/b]

- Fishnet Stockings in many colors
- You find em@ [b]Tanning Rack[/b], called [b]*Fishnet Stockings: (Color)*[/b]

- Opaque Stockings in many colors
- You find em@ [b]Tanning Rack[/b], called [b]*Opaque Stockings: (Color)*[/b]

- Bra\'s in many colors
- You find em@ [b]Tanning Rack[/b], called [b]*Bra: (Color)*[/b]
- Should match the color of Amiella Panties to wear together

- Patent Leather Stockings in Black and Brown Leather
- You find em@ [b]Tanning Rack[/b], called [b]*Leather Stockings: (Color)*[/b]

[b]!!! NOTE !!![/b] Clip in some situations in combination with tight leg armor or boots

NEW! Vendor added to Whiterun, if you\'re looking for some [b]Tinctures[/b]

Added an Option to dress the NPCs with random Panties/Stockings :)
works perfectly with [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=16877][b]No Panty Mod for Remodeled Armor CBBEv3M [/b][/url]
- To activate the option, go to console and type...
--- [b]StartQuest PantyHunter[/b] to enable, or [b]StopQuest PantyHunter[/b] to disable
--- [b]set J3XStockingsChance to x[/b] | x = 0-100, chance in % to get Stockings on NPCs
--- [b]set J3XAlwaysAdd to x[/b] | x = 0 or 1, ignores all filters, not recommended if you haven\'t some super skimpy cloths replacers installed ^^
[b]!!! NOTE !!![/b] Brawls are not working with the activated quest \"PantyHunter\", and the opponent becomes hostile when the quest is active. To fit it, stop the quest, do the brawl, and start the quest again.


[img]http://i183.photobucket.com/albums/x302/gotha83/nexus/requiredmods.png[/img]
You will need a CBBEv3M compatible body or armor mod
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=13180]CBBEv3M Body Repalacer[/url] or [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=13004]Remodeled Armor CBBEv3M [/url] for example 


[img]http://i183.photobucket.com/albums/x302/gotha83/nexus/installation.png[/img]
[b]I recommend to use NMM to install[/b]
Or drop the archive content in your Data folder, and activate the included ESP file

Endorse if you like it :)


[img]http://i183.photobucket.com/albums/x302/gotha83/nexus/changelog.png[/img]
[b]--- 2.5 ---[/b]
- added new colors to fishnet and opaque stockings
- fixed the \"empty vendor window\" issue
- changed Carolyn\'s face a bit
- deleted the stockings for boots items/recipes, because there is no use for them anymore, another patch will be available to get this kind of stockings
[b]--- 2.4 ---[/b]
- PantyHunter start/stop quest now works like intended, clean save needed if already broken quest was active
- complete crafting mechanics changed
- \"white\" base items are now craftable at [b]Tanning Rack->Leather[/b]
- after you got one of them in your inventory, you get access to recipes in other colors
- if you are missing some \"colors\" try to find Carolyn in Whiterun ;)
- feedback -> comments, but hopefully I haven\'t screwed something :D
[b]--- 2.3 ---[/b]
- added matching stockings in many colors to fit the bras/panties
- dark red color added to all panties too
- also added some leather stockings, matching the leather panty texture
- added short stockings for testing, to wear with boots for lesser clippingz: in black and white, feedback -> comments :) gonna add more colors and styles if the items works like intended. you find them in the same list like others
[b]--- 2.2 ---[/b]
- fixed black leather stockings clipping issue
- added the new panties from 2.1 to the pantyhunter quest, forgotten last time :P
[b]--- 2.1 ---[/b]
- the pantyhunter script issue with stealh gameplay is fixed
- added darker green and yellow color to the panties and bras
- added opaque stockings and patent leather stockings
[b]--- 2.0 ---[/b]
- added bras to the game in 9 different colors, craftable at the [b]tanning rack[/b]
[b]--- 1.9 ---[/b]
- added an option to dress NPCs with panties/stockings, [b]thanks to [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/users/127512]J3X[/url][/b] who made all the scripts!
- redone the lacy panty textures, to get a better look
- fixed the Stockings mesh, now all the weight settings are working!
[b]--- 1.8 ---[/b]
- added fishnet stockings, craftable at same place like other stockings
[b]--- 1.7 ---[/b]
- fixed the Panty appearance on some light sources, which were too dark/dirty looking, check the recent screenshot for details
[b]--- 1.6 ---[/b]
- added 4 Stockings in common colors, you find em at the [b]tanning rack[/b]
- Renamed the Mod from \"Craftable Pantys for CBBEv3M\" to \"Craftable Panties and Stockings for CBBEv3M\"
[b]--- 1.5 ---[/b]
- added leather and native colors to \"Panty\"
- added leather color to \"Amiella Panty\"
- added 11 new lacy textures to \"Panty\"
- You find em@ FUR category, called [b]*Lacy Panty (Color)*[/b]
- [b]Redone the whole esp: sorted out stuff which became obsolete. I recommend to unistall 1.4 first before you install 1.5 again, to get rid of dozen meshes which are unused in 1.5[/b]
- Renamed the Mod from \"17 Craftable Pantys for CBBEv3M\" to \"Craftable Pantys for CBBEv3M\"
[b]--- 1.4 ---[/b]
- ok... now really fixed the issue with the weight 100 settings!
[b]--- 1.3 ---[/b]
- fixed the clipping issue if using weight 100 settings
[b]--- 1.2 ---[/b] 
- added white color
- added a new Panty model with 8 colors
[b]--- 1.1 ---[/b] 
- added compatibility with the perks *Custom Fit* and *Well Fitted* which give a 25% bonus armor if you wear only light or heavy armor parts


[img]http://i183.photobucket.com/albums/x302/gotha83/nexus/credits.png[/img]
MAK for his Panty models and Stockings
OGFN-TEX for the Panty textures
anano for the Amiella Panty texture
Thumpbunny for leather texture
J3X for the PantyHunter Feature/Scripts
amesake for the Bra mesh


[img]http://i183.photobucket.com/albums/x302/gotha83/nexus/myothermods.png[/img]
+ [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=16877][b]No Panty Mod for Remodeled Armor CBBEv3M [/b][/url] perfect to use em together ;)


[img]http://i183.photobucket.com/albums/x302/gotha83/nexus/faq.png[/img]
Q: What skin mod are you using?
A: [url=\"http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=6554\"]CBBE skin texture V2 V3 plus Thepal and UNP compatible[/url] used this files:
\"CBBE skin texture v1_8 shaved MAIN FILE\" [size=\"3\"][b]+[/b][/size] \"CBBE skin texture v1_8 hairy trimmed body PATCH\" = result on my screens

Q: How to fix a CTD while saving the game
A: May occur on some older saves if you used earlier versions and never did a clean save before upgrading to new version, [b]Vonpire[/b] describes a solution [url=\"http://forums.nexusmods.com/index.php?/topic/671089-8-craftable-pantys-for-cbbev3m/page__view__findpost__p__6068271\"][b]here[/b][/url], how he fixed it on his savegame, try it
